N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5102.6 - Minimum employee age

State Regulations

No natural person under the age of 18 years shall be
eligible to receive a license from the commission as a video lottery gaming key
employee, video lottery gaming employee or principal of a vendor or be
authorized as a temporary service provider. Notes
